Class TermsDataSource

    • it.unipd.dei.eis.data.sources.DataSource<TermsDataEntity,Map<String,Integer>>

  • public class TermsDataSource
extends DataSource<TermsDataEntity,Map<String,Integer>>
    TermsDataSource is the data source for the terms. It contains the data structure of the terms.
